1989;;Lost Angels;;American;;Hugh Hudson;;Donald Sutherland;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lost_Angels_(1989_film);;Tim Doolan (Horovitz), a troubled youth from a broken home in Los Angeles, is sent to a private psychiatric hospital after an altercation with the police turns violent. In the hospital, he makes a connection with Dr. Charles Loftis (Sutherland), a man with issues of his own.